relationships.target: 中华人民共和国国务院

description.zh-cn: 江西省人民政府是中华人民共和国国务院领导下的地方国家行政机关。
description.en: The Jiangxi Provincial People's Government is a local state administrative organ under the leadership of the State Council of the People's Republic of China.

description.zh-cn: 江西省人民政府由江西省人民代表大会产生，对它负责，受它监督。
description.en: The Jiangxi Provincial People's Government is produced by, responsible to, and supervised by the Jiangxi Provincial People's Congress.

relationships.target: 江西省人民代表大会常务委员会

description.zh-cn: 江西省人民代表大会闭会期间，江西省人民政府对江西省人民代表大会常务委员会负责并报告工作。
description.en: When the Jiangxi Provincial People's Congress is not in session, the Jiangxi Provincial People's Government is responsible to and reports its work to the Standing Committee of the Jiangxi Provincial People's Congress.

description.zh-cn: 1955年2月，江西省人民政府改组为江西省人民委员会。
description.en: In February 1955, the Jiangxi Provincial People's Government was reorganized into the Jiangxi Provincial People's Committee.

description.zh-cn: 1968年1月，江西省人民委员会改组为江西省革命委员会。
description.en: In January 1968, the Jiangxi Provincial People's Committee was reorganized into the Jiangxi Provincial Revolutionary Committee.

description.zh-cn: 1979年12月，江西省革命委员会复称江西省人民政府。
description.en: In December 1979, the Jiangxi Provincial Revolutionary Committee was renamed back to the Jiangxi Provincial People's Government.
